      },
      "type": "term",
      "surface": {
        "jp": "復号",
        "zh": "解密",
        "en": "Decryption"
      },
      "definition": {
        "jp": "暗号文を平文に戻すこと。ITパスポート試験では「復号化」とはいわず、単に「復号」という。",
        "zh": "将密文还原为明文。在IT护照考试中不称为「解密化」，仅称为「解密」。",
        "en": "Restoring ciphertext back into plaintext. In the IT Passport exam, it is not called \"decryption-ization\" but simply \"decryption\"."
      },
      "kana_helper": null
    },
    {
      "id": "itpassport_r6::term::p530::2",
      "anchor": {
        "page": 530,
        "block_id": "page_530_block_2",
        "section_path": []
      },
      "type": "term",
      "surface": {
        "jp": "ディスク暗号化",
        "zh": "磁盘加密",
        "en": "Disk Encryption"
      },
      "definition": {
        "jp": "HDDやSSDなどの補助記憶装置の中のデータを丸ごと暗号化すること。",
        "zh": "将硬盘驱动器（HDD）、固态硬盘（SSD）等辅助存储器中的数据整体加密。",
        "en": "Encrypting all data in auxiliary storage devices such as HDD or SSD in its entirety."
      },
      "kana_helper": null
    },
    {
      "id": "itpassport_r6::term::p530::3",
      "anchor": {
